.DT
setmin
Discworld creator help
setmin

.SH Name
.SI 5
setmin - Set your movement messages.
EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
setmin <message>
setmout <message>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Set your entry/exit message.  You can only use this command if you have
completed the quest that gives this ability as a reward.  The commands are
setmin and setmout.  Setmin sets the message given when you enter a room and
setmout sets the message printed when you leave.

PLEASE KEEP YOUR ENTRY/EXIT MESSAGES IN THEME WITH DISCWORLD!
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
setmin wanders in
setmout wanders away
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
setmmin, review
.EI
